      <div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn">
        <p><lb n="1"></lb>kō-vicaiya-ciṅ <lb break="no" n="2"></lb>kaviṇṇa-parumaṟku muppat-āvatu</p>
        <p>nī <lb break="no" n="3"></lb>lakaṇṭarai <gap quantity="5" reason="undefined" unit="character"></gap> kal poṉṉumū <lb break="no" n="4"></lb>taṉ<unclear>ṉā</unclear> <gap quantity="3" reason="undefined" unit="character"></gap> koṭiyaṉ <lb break="no" n="5"></lb>ṉūru Eṟinta <unclear>ñā</unclear>ṉṟu <lb n="6"></lb>kaṅkaru makkaḷ po <lb break="no" n="7"></lb>ṉṉakkaṉāru cēvaka <lb break="no" n="8"></lb>ṉ vāṇakō-<choice>
            <orig>A</orig>
            <reg>y-a</reg>
          </choice>tiraicaru <lb n="9"></lb>makkaḷ poṉ<unclear>ṉi</unclear>revaru <lb n="10"></lb>Eṟintu paṭṭāṉ</p>
        <p>Iru <lb break="no" n="11"></lb>-<unclear>p</unclear>-perum maṟaiya <gap quantity="2" reason="undefined" unit="character"></gap> maka <lb break="no" n="12"></lb>ṉ putaṉ kal</p>
      </div>
